2.5 COMMERCIAL DATAFLEX SPLF SERVER CONNECTION LICENSE The DataFlex SPLF Server Connection License is an add-on entitlement for a DataFlex WebApp Server. The license entitles a DataFlex WebApp Server to connect to the security, performance, load balancing and failover resources of an SPLF server. Each WebApp application server connected to an SPLF Server requires its own SPLF Server Connection License. 

